description: Unassigns the specified secondary private IP addresses or IPv4 Prefix Delegation prefixes from a network interface.

parameters.name: Ipv4Prefixes
parameters.description: The IPv4 prefixes to unassign from the network interface. (string) ---

parameters.name: NetworkInterfaceId
parameters.description: The ID of the network interface.

parameters.name: PrivateIpAddresses
parameters.description: The secondary private IP addresses to unassign from the network interface. You can specify this option multiple times to unassign more than one IP address. (string) ---
